---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About | The Pulse Paper"
  description="What The Pulse Paper is, why it exists, and how often it ships."
>
  <section class="wrap-narrow about">
    <h1>About The Pulse Paper</h1>

    <p>
      The Pulse Paper is independent analysis of Pakistan&rsquo;s economy, markets, and
      supply chains. It exists to do one thing well: explain what is actually moving &mdash;
      and what it means for the people who make decisions with money.
    </p>

    <p>
      Pakistan produces no shortage of economic commentary. What it lacks is timely,
      rigorous analysis that connects global forces &mdash; oil benchmarks, the dollar,
      interest rates, commodity cycles &mdash; to their concrete consequences for businesses,
      investors, and operators here. That connection is the entire job of this publication.
    </p>

    <h2>What you get</h2>
    <p>
      The weekly edition is a single, focused brief: what moved, what&rsquo;s developing, and
      what to do about it. Alongside the editions, free standalone articles cover individual
      topics in depth &mdash; open to read and share.
    </p>

    <h2>The rhythm</h2>
    <p>
      A full edition every Sunday. Free articles whenever something is worth writing about.
      A monthly roll-up with a longer outlook.
    </p>

    <div class="about-cta">
      <a href="/#subscribe" class="cta-btn">Subscribe &mdash; it&rsquo;s free</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about { padding-top: 48px; }
    .about h1 { font-size: 34px; margin: 0 0 22px; }
    .about h2 { font-size: 21px; margin: 32px 0 10px; }
    .about p { font-size: 17px; margin: 0 0 18px; }
    .about-cta { margin-top: 36px; }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block; background: var(--accent); color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 15px;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--accent-dark); }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about { padding-top: 32px; }
      .about h1 { font-size: 26px; }
      .about h2 { font-size: 18px; }
      .about p { font-size: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</Base>
